    {
      "id": "1924750c-f3ba-8026-b02b-d2cada50223f",
      "type": "paragraph",
      "text": "Group work is a common strategy employed to improve learning outcomes and common strategies is random formation. The work proposes a Moodle Plugin that automates group foprmation using ML. ",
      "raw": {
        "object": "block",
        "id": "1924750c-f3ba-8026-b02b-d2cada50223f",
        "parent": {
          "type": "page_id",
