    {
      "id": "1924750c-f3ba-80ab-9518-fcb6d8788db1",
      "type": "paragraph",
      "text": "The plugin uses clustering to identify homogenous groups that share “similare behaviours”. Then, selection of members from different groups is done in order to ensure heterogeneity. Abstract makes no mention of empyrical results.",
